From 2d39402669ce371960a639a991644b890ce666a7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Wed, 22 Jul 2026 19:04:13 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] scaffold: initial workspace, UI shell, server skeleton,
 deploy configs

- npm workspaces monorepo: client (Vite+TS), server (Fastify+TS+Postgres), shared types
- Client: login + main menu HTML/CSS in dark emerald theme, screen manager, no game logic yet
- Server: Fastify skeleton with /api/health, role middleware, Postgres pool wiring
- Tooling: TypeScript strict, ESLint (typescript-eslint strict+stylistic), Prettier, husky + lint-staged
- Build: Vite with Terser + javascript-obfuscator (heavy, prod only)
- Deploy: nginx configs for rykochet.io + dev.rykochet.io with Cloudflare real-IP, PM2 ecosystem for prod:3000 + dev:3001
- Postgres schema: accounts, sessions, bans, maps, staff_actions audit log, recordings, fingerprint + IP history
